      "asbval:note": "Paper discusses filtering poor quality peaks and provides visualizations of quality metrics, but does not explicitly describe generating a 'row count comparison report' with specific filenames. The concept of comparing filtered vs. unfiltered feature counts is present but not as a named deliverable.",
