    {
      "@id": "asbval:assertion/card/10_1038_s41467_023_39889_1__task_004/006",
      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "Global visualization of these three quality metrics in Yeast2021 data, in relation to peak size, is shown in Fig. 6c... The SNR distribution is an informative way to assess how much useful information is in a metabolomics dataset (Fig. 6d\u2013f, Supplementary Fig. 9b).",
