      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "To test the scalability, we subset the SLAW data using varying sample numbers. The CPU time and memory use was largely a linear function of sample numbers (Fig. 8b, c). The results indicate that the performance gap between XCMS and asari widens for larger studies.",
      "asbval:note": "Paper explicitly investigates scalability of asari with varying sample numbers, measuring both CPU time and memory usage.",
