    {
      "@id": "asbval:assertion/skill/computational-resource-profiling-and-benchmarking/005",
      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "Asari is designed with a set of distinct algorithmic framework and data structures, and all steps are explicitly trackable. The software is open source on GitHub and available via standard Python package management tools, which can be integrated seamlessly with cloud deployment.",
      "asbval:note": "Paper confirms asari is a Python-based tool available via Python package management, but does not specify Python 3.8+ as a requirement in the provided passages.",
