      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "The default peak detection algorithm in asari first estimates the baseline and noise level... We use a local maximum search algorithm, with peak height and prominence requirements dynamically determined on the segment statistics.",
      "asbval:note": "Paper states asari uses a 'local maximum search algorithm', not scipy.signal.find_peaks. This is a different implementation than claimed.",
